Documentation

Script Functionality

	1.	Webhook URL: Specifies the Discord webhook URL where the password is sent for further analysis.
	2.	Custom Figlet Banner: Displays a custom figlet banner with the script name.
	3.	Main Title Display: Displays the main title of the script.
	4.	User Input: Prompts the user to enter the password to be tested.
	5.	File Writing: Writes the user-provided password to a file for processing.
	6.	Password Sending: Sends the password to the specified Discord webhook for analysis.
	7.	Password Guessing: Brute-forces the password character by character using itertools.product.
	8.	Progress Bar: Displays a progress bar indicating the number of attempts made.
	9.	Output Display: Prints the guessed password and the number of attempts it took.
	10.	Exit Prompt: Prompts the user to press enter before exiting.

Troubleshooting

	•	If the script fails to execute, ensure that the required dependencies (requests, tqdm, pyfiglet) are installed.
	•	Check network connectivity for sending data to the Discord webhook.

For any further assistance or inquiries, please contact the script author.
